{"title":"准备后事","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备后事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载：美国防部指定了科学机构专门研究在什么条件下投降的问题。消息传出，舆论哗然，弄得艾森豪威尔大为难堪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国丑闻本不少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筹备投降事更妙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秘密泄露太难听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只得彻查又辟谣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还没有打仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先研究投降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥时举手，怎么求饶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备后事苦思量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远看瞪眼吹胡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近看篾片浆糊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是：拆穿西洋镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只纸老虎！（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江有生　插图"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}